{"h70a10ad4gdbe0g45d1gb835gfc4cdbe129f2": ["You made it. Come here - sit with me.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "523a509b-315c-45a7-505a-030dbbe2ea55"], "h1d36c5e6g2c26g477ega0bcg7db6fc54bacc": ["What do you have in mind? Besides the bottle, that is.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "4a6d0384-040a-7886-5fbd-f7f07fedb777"], "haf1ac02agbbe6g4186gb534g4d4cddf6fd5c": ["Well to begin, I think a toast is in order. Any suggestions?", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "b1117253-57f5-0d22-597d-3892df2e8904"], "h745ed607g0679g44c2g90b0g1d1369babe1b": ["To victory.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "2517eb63-8aeb-ad51-ca89-b6952d9bdf15"], "h546c8c33g2ecfg4cf4gbbedgbc2c449b1d8d": ["Dominant, self-centred, savouring another's loss...", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "a57f14d6-59f4-480e-925d-8960633aa3a7"], "hb5ee1c69g6737g4082g994cg6608f9d25db4": ["... I like it. To victory.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "f88078cf-c361-8e0b-8a3e-21c441dbf1ba"], "h27b955f3gd6c8g4d14gb310g4bc116e8e188": ["Now tell me something about yourself.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "0a38c9a7-eda2-fc8c-586e-98121101f6cf"], "h617bd580g6327g44a9g9ff2g9a5073da8c90": ["And no tadpoles, dragons, marauding goblins, or anything like that. Something about <i>you</i>.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "101101c0-aa11-6f0e-9bed-5d1ca1de8cf5"], "hdfb3a1e7g4287g4c73ga022ga093ddc2a83b": ["Something about me? I'm surprised you cared.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "ace04ce9-aa11-467f-6d2b-0c335c5c579a"], "h5fc46622g8d4dg43bfg9259gb38c8fa0a749": ["Fishing for blackmail material, that's all.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "87ac6107-b343-b779-6d73-240fbd914e3a"], "h7be19c23gc29cg4780gaf11g1d9cae9e03fe": ["Go on - I insist.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "9bce45a3-a381-4ec6-9965-5d8c39c124b5"], "h290a80eegb859g4018g98f8g57c435cc09a4": ["<i>Tell her about your death - how you'd been attacked by a Gur tribe and 'saved' by Cazador.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "0de2d313-5399-356f-2be8-bfdf89357e4c"], "hf06e7d8dg60f8g437dg87a5g9458be2cbb9a": ["How morbid. Yet fascinating.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "8ed313e9-5bf8-cf3f-8ce1-19edcd6f2775"], "hcd3cab6fg3572g4456g8702g49902ddd45cc": ["Don't stop now. Not just as things are getting interesting...", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "60b69572-8d12-e494-571d-2a2d4aeef104"], "hef92cf5ag5629g4651g9adeg3e06a04258bd": ["I'm not sure what else I can say.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "a82bb017-da5e-e2ab-f031-ec9223635611"], "h1da8ba2ag70b0g4144g92cfge8153cef2a87": ["Sounds like you just need a little more liquid inspiration.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "0103e29b-b1ca-132d-c831-2929c0e7ab6d"], "h364232dfg862bg4d2dgbaf8gf54172c3bc91": ["Your turn - I insist. A little give and take is only fair.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "89fb2c89-e35c-e1c6-2f0c-18f0482f3f58"], "hf203d96bgec1fg4129gb4e9g57f5a5302a1c": ["Don't laugh... but I'm not quite sure I have anything to share.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "81371e3d-a514-4b8c-4e97-aa9b7fc7ed34"], "h5bdd089eged12g445fgb82cg7683e06a69f5": ["When you worship Shar, secrecy is everything. We'll sacrifice our own memories when ordered to.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "d441112e-b65f-e9a5-ee74-0da55f86320e"], "ha40b080cg85bdg4b1fgbaa5gadd79a842d3e": ["A lot of the little things... they're lost to me right now.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "1349993a-5f89-927a-6218-f1dafd096ee6"], "h842a2d2cg50f4g4d8dgaf8cg4a8efc51c3b6": ["But your memories are coming back, aren't they?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "13bdd504-3d00-3e62-97a7-638eb6428a61"], "h57885d7ag32fag4870g94f1gbd09d8288436": ["Perhaps, but please - enough about me. Sharing's bad for my complexion.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "74af23c6-9a0f-5e5c-ee9c-bee49e754f71"], "h8956a844g0814g481dgbb10g6f945a33ac06": ["There's still plenty of wine and the whole night ahead of us.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "f942b94b-68e2-f898-d647-08d6d2845f59"], "hf11ba7fbg84dfg4f0eg8bdbgddeb015c8334": ["Nearly light. The others will be awake soon...", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "45e17618-65cb-dd84-65df-fe59eac4d2d6"], "ha3afc731g3003g4425gacefg35de9648a4f1": ["<i>Look into her eyes.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "d42e5cb5-1a8b-dc2a-c110-47ca0efdbfc4"], "h81a5d4f2g74c0g43a4ga8a3gb8c814daa6ef": ["What?", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "be1c29e1-86ba-576d-4e76-baf0ae1b1f2a"], "hdaf5e53bg6f82g40b9g999egda2449774b02": ["You're beautiful.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "27236643-6444-f589-48fb-e54a8eec81d6"], "he1919baag3161g49begb699gd19091d50814": ["I know.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "d0808c04-d91a-3acc-1024-4b0fc467032e"], "h2020545dg230eg4cc9gbed6gcc39a20de442": ["But you're sweet to notice.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "12f2dba1-c52d-1757-1b37-bd41e68a9a71"], "hcfe466degc353g4b3cg9621g45fb715fa34b": ["Thank you for last night.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "8b42334c-08fb-afc8-9ac6-c714a1d9dba5"], "h723e55c7ga89fg4566g8764gaf9d28f83026": ["I hope there'll be more to come.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "022a51e2-ec71-7d19-da92-63415bb7a767"], "h76c1bf5agee92g4d9eg8c79g972820306963": ["Me too.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "0dfabaf6-fa1e-e748-7eb7-2060ee922b64"], "h66665949gc37cg4601g9e2cga5acc6f8e848": ["*She trails off. You read an invitation in her eyes.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "2dcd9250-7479-a6a4-302d-dfe5ea05dfc1"], "h9f06ccb2ga12fg4e89g8745gc1417a5bcd16": ["<i>Kiss her.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "38d76bc7-8832-cd03-5baa-59ecda72941d"], "h73909e49gb47cg447cga1feg7486b5e4a014": ["That didn't hurt, did it?", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "a493c923-3b3a-7ab8-f8bd-9d2ce7a8734a"], "hb00e68b1g1b28g4625g8e2cgd287de2d0c38": ["No. Far from it.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "eb63c5e6-c72f-5f93-cd6d-4a2bb6ea5b1a"], "h7655637ag94dag4f16g8437gaeba16434ad2": ["Good to know. For the future...", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "4ae4a70d-e3c7-8368-c401-18d19755004e"], "h20fcc9a2g89d1g4677gbd6fg94e0342af4ea": ["Let's head back. If we must.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "f7540901-e9b4-b5a9-cd97-dca93d0b8a31"], "h8e4bd0c8gb6f3g482aga8c5ga68fd21d2749": ["The pain was worth it.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "2f814009-9587-89cf-bec9-d214e80a335f"], "h72c94fb9g68bbg46f3gb006gfa8094bdeefd": ["I should think so.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "77051ad8-3b65-e733-5cb2-06c47740853d"], "h892af949ga824g4ff2g9a94geb21bd862a33": ["A little tingle.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "458cd6e7-458c-123f-7ec4-a70d344edfb1"], "hc64d2846g86f2g4d55g9806g8aebf7d3b49f": ["I'd like to think that would've happened anyway.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "78bfff24-c63e-7b54-6e7a-3c9c66b3b7bb"], "h128d7654g25b3g452fg9aedgf0387c0690e1": ["You know, if you want something... I think you should take it.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "2ca76033-15ff-5763-296b-2800bc1930d2"], "h06032b79gf7fag4e52g8b96g01c7f8804ead": ["<i>Let the moment pass.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "8aeb732a-8655-186c-6d20-7746ce613556"], "hf9502448g187ag4815g932fgf8aa7733cafb": ["I... we should head back.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "7081a62e-65c3-b658-449e-95fcaf1c8c2c"], "h9014cb25g7feeg4c97ga4b5g1dd165f05abc": ["We should do this again some time.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "6b0332e5-b90d-8e3a-b5d3-0c5bf8d3331c"], "he1f22237gc260g4213g88e4g33f1aecf1647": ["Oh... yes. I suppose we'll have to.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "5381f4b0-8ec4-cfaf-1076-073ee520a0e0"], "h4d0e7e26gd7c3g4b55gbabag2d9bcced46f5": ["We should head back.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "43336d3d-ee97-c752-5c8b-0dcfb217093c"], "h80670f96gd4aag4ec0g89e7g18fa1d31a742": ["We should head back.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "4db6be8f-1737-e0f9-bfb8-ae720eb97cd3"], "h0385fbadg2d76g43baga8abg4e5baf9b0708": ["Oh... of course.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "ac6ba271-5649-fac8-643f-e4f67a31ffff"], "h12f186fcgf67eg4734ga365g572a4c51b5ac": ["My pleasure.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "93e55e5a-7860-6a0c-17bc-1e63fbd52d79"], "h48fdcab2g5a95g452agb91age33609a91754": ["It was just what I needed.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "33791312-c648-9622-797c-de0d3a108eee"], "ha6c5563fgbc21g419dg8d9fg7697a6037d71": ["There's no need to thank me.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "2a6ea2ff-cbc2-226a-c4c6-2fde66cfdab3"], "hbd133bdcg4fc4g404fg9e97gf20d70bbe545": ["Well deserved, though.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "c3357d87-6283-6b37-962b-958534347458"], "h29c86f2cg3991g4741g8fe8g3a65e09669da": ["Just checking for signs of ceremorphosis.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "ee706f81-2a3e-0acc-b588-7011dcaee4da"], "h378724d0g0842g43e2g8cf1g01a517ae5d66": ["Oh, I'm perfectly fine, but the mood is well and truly dead.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "5ff2c4d6-2801-0629-6fad-cdd57492ac10"], "ha1755205g5c08g4ad5g985bgc39c9dad395f": ["Anyway. Thank you for tonight.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "4c794825-7ccf-102d-06f2-ed8440feb160"], "h1c7420fegc90dg45e5gb07dg2c925c4112f2": ["Never mind.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "e08e2b56-1136-7df4-4f8d-e2a84e31dd6f"], "hc29cd5b8g093ag4091gb3f4g5e252b06a6b9": ["Bashful come the light of day?", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "02985796-df83-f63d-53f0-dab17c500318"], "h28b26c02g5265g4617g811dg64cbbc1801ab": ["The others can wait. I don't want this to end just yet.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "df859d3a-8004-b4c3-4cce-3b8eec23cff1"], "h1f82cb10gb01bg4e7bgb470g8ee0f7180542": ["Another moment won't kill them, I suppose... well, it might, but let's take that risk.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "1bd621c1-2c26-e633-04a7-b6007a2ef959"], "h2ffcd31cgf880g46b8gba3fg1ae74b511bb6": ["We should get back then.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "f27a148b-f841-1431-b9f0-2caf4acf639a"], "h9da3333dg3318g4fd8g8a3dgd3b790fa70fa": ["I suppose so. Celebration's over, time to pick up the trail again.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "a9332e78-1934-517b-32df-1e2e43009935"], "hfe3abafcg4babg48e2gbd30g348ccca9e229": ["Do you think your memories will ever come back?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "ad6b0f05-6381-2393-3a5b-18e9179b66c1"], "h40e0b3e2gccdbg4994g95b4g5041b50efd6b": ["Wrong. You like night orchids and can't swim. You told me once.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "cd0f7b17-1fe7-c28f-a2b8-b7a488a457d1"], "h190d0f0eg9176g42bagaeadg52027f8bc48b": ["Heh, I did! And you remembered. ", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "79467a52-416e-acdc-cf86-468c5b10832e"], "hce3a94b3gd851g4f86ga9f0g4c720ad7c639": ["You're sweet.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "c559cb46-cdfd-53a5-1976-c3cdfb368f94"], "h0eeeade0g425fg4c57g82e1g94ea5a1c2e65": ["Drinking wine won't help that.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "9621496d-0b97-f041-bf71-11fafbb2ba97"], "h2e4a2dcfg316dg48dbga3b7g3da466948b45": ["On the contrary.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "1906af55-8ae3-510a-6b90-e5e9065ffa04"], "h1966fb38g2829g470egac53gffe7a527b2f3": ["It helps me create all new memories.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "02960967-b62d-cf4b-736c-43999433345c"], "hb57ff7cbgf6b6g481cg89bfg4f2e27c52927": ["That's a convenient way to avoid the question.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "b55e3c80-37b1-06c3-dcf8-9734390c0482"], "hfd834919g8497g47dbga912g20168e26b967": ["It's not convenient - it's true.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "09e73dc9-547b-b6d3-032a-a06e4ffb22bd"], "h41e2f70dgcac1g4bd7g8a8cgc25128f3e4be": ["But please - enough about me. Sharing's bad for my complexion.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "8ee10c06-9713-568d-a3c8-7c236698e9c4"], "ha449cd85gc68eg435ag957fg27b269891b5b": ["Where I come from, that's frowned upon.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "2e125273-76ac-d33d-39ae-3a1697731873"], "hc3f634a1gd12eg4292g9d30gd1286e49e06a": ["What, you're discouraged from confiding? Talking about your feelings? Sounds... lonely.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "43600435-e7a5-c18a-3d4b-1ca132c0457c"], "hfe90c347gc68ag44bdg9effgb409f4d01d77": ["Which is why I'm looking for a little company.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "e166e1a0-401f-054b-9bec-f6b770bec0f7"], "h881d4096ga770g4500ga8efg11ded91a2502": ["You have me curious now.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "9d1fca4f-6023-1c34-f718-c9bd5260b55e"], "h143289ccgb21dg422dga467gf2c35c02c2b5": ["Good. A little mystery will keep you on your toes.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "9007fac5-c402-6e47-1a29-6ec741377489"], "h09184809g4fc8g4281gbebeg509ca4fea132": ["Fair enough. I didn't mean to pry.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "28cb785f-b0f9-0169-09d1-54dc3390e8e0"], "hf68b9931g5685g4c11ga6c8g5cac70b85be3": ["Oh? And what else do you find to be fair?", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "e2e8cf67-f437-b17b-36fb-9c9f13948a64"], "h17e793d7g1b53g453fgab77gf9f6b5e57dfa": ["Honestly? You.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "f731104c-ef12-be1c-c844-f7fcb7f35433"], "h8a068db5gfd71g4b2dg91f5g959e9654c0b7": ["You don't waste time, do you?", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "655ec5b7-949e-da91-fb0b-08edc340e5ce"], "ha65ec6cfgd320g4d45g8a0eg9001e9de29d1": ["Straight answers. Got any for me?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "4e87b84c-061e-a265-eaae-b2c0020f2637"], "he6a19800gbf01g4ed3g85afg405ce76933ff": ["Straight answers are overrated. Where's the discovery?", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "60c17536-d65d-2818-5e98-0454f8af6885"], "h046d115bg2edfg4cefg935bg5719250ca7af": ["<i>Smile and say nothing.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "65a790f2-fe55-daae-e05d-a4718d96358a"], "hed6a6682gc067g4069gb4f6geb00b553d2fd": ["Oh, I see. Think I can't get you to confess? I'm something of an expert.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "ce225c6b-1d95-7895-c54d-25d7bc0873e9"], "h69bb670fg9962g44a8g8794gb20ffcf518e6": ["We should head back. We might be missed.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "89d26f8b-eed0-f442-8031-fdc5ccacbc7a"], "he00d8dccg1d93g4f2dgb731ga4920676ec8c": ["I'm sure they'd last another while without us. But if you insist...", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "ea58d72f-7398-49db-2255-0e3175de4e79"], "h82377976ga30eg43feg8e29gbdbd6aee75a5": ["I suppose there's not that much of a rush.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "7cd1248a-d2b6-c642-7aa3-b5c7298b79f1"], "hcf918088g827bg439dga3d0g7f4b84825b1b": ["Nothing worthwhile should be rushed anyway.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "296b4198-7940-6249-0db0-0676614b8d67"], "h95b780b1g19b4g4a8egb18eg69714557cfb7": ["I insist.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "22c85ba6-7bc9-5efb-5ece-5eabc441d212"], "ha507d3b2g994dg4f8fga506g84fb7c6b0563": ["Well then. Head on back. I'm sure your cold bedroll is missing you terribly.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "a69ec07a-c1eb-1e17-8516-c1725a27b65c"], "h25799c09gdca4g48eegbedfgea5ac833bb60": ["<i>Tell her the darkness inside of you wasn't caused by an accident. It was done out of love for someone.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "4c34b2d7-5a49-f0b6-e9ae-807fb754d41a"], "h7ebf0981gf601g4463g974fgaef43af7d8ac": ["Does that mean you're spoken for, or not? Heh.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "f5ddb3f7-161d-832b-e849-6be8e63aeeea"], "h83340fb1g6a43g4f62gaed8g2b550199aac5": ["|I shared a little something about myself. Nothing too wild, but personal|", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "f1cdeafa-fb0b-32fe-c681-e78e4b175c69"], "h9f0428cbg1fbfg4d90g8fd1geba695837036": ["_", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "bf6cc301-76c2-5ca5-7544-9cbd50aa296f"], "hfd4b71aagea37g45e1g863cg3ca1bf8b4b81": ["|I shared a little something about myself. Nothing too wild, but personal|", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "eed46f0d-24ad-c5cb-6a7b-e3c1e60efff7"], "h8202e6b8g0cd6g4080g8fe6g370f634bbdb1": ["|Why thank you for your candor, Karlach. Persuading me to share something about myself will now be 50% easier, though I'll still want to hear more about you first.|", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "cf92c703-641a-c391-a533-8a9624955c13"], "h1c1797c7g8cc4g485bga378g2d23493db666": ["<i>Lower your guard, and describe the desolate beauty of your home: Cr\u00e8che K'liir.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "b58e9616-b47a-893d-5676-2fc41dbf1914"], "h4461f143ge507g453egae20g0683ebcc909b": ["Merciless, but beautiful in its own way... sounds familiar.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "f767180b-e66e-99d4-4f62-ad94a9f0fd8d"], "hc10b47d7g4c86g49ccgac98g86db63915f8f": ["|I shared a little something about myself. Nothing too wild, but personal|", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "4d03b8da-b34b-bdc0-cdfb-1b1cb8af7bfa"], "h11f5f63eg82aag44aag96f0g07b456dffec9": ["|Why thank you for your candor, Misnc. Persuading me to share something about myself will now be 50% easier, though I'll still want to hear more about you first.|", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "c14933bf-d22b-469c-32f7-80ad97b89326"], "hdd6d7f87ge16fg438ag9221gc4463e0738fa": ["<i>Relate Mizora's hold over you - and your eagerness to be free.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "a7ca590f-f630-695f-52c2-75a737dcda06"], "h2c0fa450g4ffag4f78g9726g3ae7726f6bbb": ["<i>Speak of your wealthy father, and the myriad ways you've disappointed him.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "c72181b2-ac38-615c-b080-bcdf03ee12fa"], "h31653076g8c06g4081g9f17g0441e5ed84e8": ["Don't worry. I'm sure there's plenty of things you excel at that your father isn't privy to...", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "a0f3e3f2-7ec0-cc15-95cb-a28dc98cf2de"], "h00ce2f28g2084g423eg8cf5g139233955a28": ["<i>Speak of dedication to your clan above all else. A life of honour and duty that supersedes even blood.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "a067f07c-30b3-d7bf-4f82-9df6f1d07765"], "h9f19ca8eg86d2g4e82g8ebcg9c0bd151a21f": ["I can respect that sort of loyalty. It's not all that removed from what was instilled in me...", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "e0ff56a9-8da3-9a05-b327-2ac66686558c"], "hdfdb71dag1e9eg4f14g8addgc08b4be54fed": ["<i>Speak of an uncertain youth, neither fully at home with humans or orcs. A youth that forged resilience, self-reliance.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "4b762f2f-8374-1dd1-b2c4-785cd60655ce"], "h6f270a53gbf03g419ag9f55ge0fee516d305": ["I can sympathise, truly.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "5f82db63-819d-089c-76de-5bcff01c7d76"], "h731d8d15g48deg458fga928g90a47972648f": ["<i>Share memories of growing up in the Underdark.<br></i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "a9917ee0-e07b-5929-cce0-e220f4229fd7"], "hacf465a1gc634g4f03gb1d8gccb212a54fa5": ["<i>Share some memories from your youth. The fight to survive, to prove yourself.<br></i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "a9917ee0-e07b-5929-cce0-e220f4229fd7"], "hcfa44b62gb1c3g4bf0g9abbg0eaeb3191953": ["<i>Share a little memory from growing up in Baldur's Gate.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "a9917ee0-e07b-5929-cce0-e220f4229fd7"], "h104a6fcag67d0g4f10ga138g827a60c2332c": ["You must have an extraordinary affinity for the darkness. I'm jealous.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "d1c412c4-ff85-594d-7d3d-a7c3a19c4fec"], "h1e4d0f31g2e6dg48ffga135g2157b734a87e": ["Whatever I said about your kind before, trust I'll never accuse you of being boring.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "d1c412c4-ff85-594d-7d3d-a7c3a19c4fec"], "hcbcf9842gab7cg4e80gab32gc2aec387bf9d": ["Seems like you truly know the city. I never got to explore it to my liking.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "d1c412c4-ff85-594d-7d3d-a7c3a19c4fec"], "h072bf34fg066bg4bb1g8b4bg0f1811b0fc19": ["There's other things we could do besides talk.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "b2522958-b643-90d0-d220-355bf687a03f"], "hf1f8de37g4458g460dgbd70g8db4ddc0c3eb": ["Oh I'm aware. Several come to mind right now... but I'm going to tempt fate and say we can take our time.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "1c0bf19a-c48f-34c4-c703-7abcbcb8dfe1"], "hff202b7agb5fcg4cd3g9191gd01b7399e0f9": ["You first.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "f962209c-352e-1747-b5cc-815478e64249"], "ha499238dgcbf2g4c5cga3a5gc52c8788e389": ["Oh no. I provided the refreshments. You can supply the entertainment.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "0a84751f-207f-1d74-67b9-b4924125cccf"], "hed7fa441g3621g4c49g8dd9gf4f6497ec671": ["You can be tricky sometimes, you know.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "debc5dd7-9489-d97b-5524-667d097e6920"], "hb49c533eg10feg443egafd3g0f6392693e57": ["I know. One of my many fine qualities.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "1d1eb5cc-c5c2-8c7d-b07b-8db455b04efd"], "hb9bda12egbfaeg4f91gb134g82242837ffc9": ["<i>Thank her for the wine and leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "12add19b-cca9-1ba2-8a44-d51dd5b94bd9"], "h31586628gcf10g48f8gbda4g15002aa4a9dd": ["You... all right, then. More the fool me.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "b0400084-c413-b8ca-bb74-7fc6e47c40fa"], "hd95d4cf2g7cbdg4fc0gaf92g203cadfbf9fe": ["To survival.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "8b69ed85-a65b-aff3-b59c-745d2a13a9c7"], "h78e879fdg3787g4973gab8cg854874cd6826": ["Very practical. We could've toasted to that every night so far.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "b270c2f2-2caf-fd9c-b41c-e5821f45ffb9"], "h326748e0gc2adg4230gba72g7ff3473a0f0c": ["Here's to many more. Survival.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "cdc21051-6dbb-f087-5521-c882f230d559"], "hd163de70g4f56g457fgb044gcc93e5c63833": ["To us.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "cf7a1507-98c2-0812-39f2-5796fcad1dce"], "h3f615a62gd4bcg4158gb5f8g9caf4f551563": ["Bold. What does 'us' entail?", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "9cc525b1-daeb-766b-864a-4bb45fe52ec6"], "h237bad19g50abg4ddfgb2dag7b6d680e8a0c": ["I suppose I'll find out. To us.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "b7bff6db-e3cf-e029-e8ba-fa83ba700be6"], "h8ae4162cg77e9g4b99g96c3g7945b35d8471": ["To friendship.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "3b8248e7-59b4-81a7-11cd-facf5defebeb"], "hf1e0a639g5d9bg43a4g96a4gc2117921f978": ["Right. 'Friendship.'", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "dd9daace-497d-005d-8cea-a3571c210d1b"], "he949106ag16ceg4cc2gbc79g1eac1d028b02": ["Very well, have it your way. To friendship.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "7c31a0f9-cf01-5f4c-4cff-8b53f61e4b43"], "hec95e830g24e5g4defg84c6gce61fc6680ee": ["I seem to recall a campful of goblins faring very poorly after a toast.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "bede54bc-5f39-3892-04f0-70cf623bdca1"], "h47a5a14cgbf21g4d23g9c10gb130b6f77766": ["Heh. Not worried, are you? Rest easy.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "2d6c9439-64b5-de49-0b7e-8580fcdd6221"], "h864a4bbdga40cg41c3g9b71g43474db8eb93": ["To not being poisoned - how about that?", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "ba27f696-5758-7997-0fcc-7134f3293c03"], "hbdbd830cg9c76g412bga03dgbd4639144a3d": ["<i>Shrug and drink deeply.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "1b666476-d49f-7d5c-2fad-bfaeb328d3b0"], "h96c4eea1g86a0g4f44ga3bege23e0b74100f": ["Not one for taking things slowly, I see.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "fe41ec0f-8acb-816f-6622-0bb5ec376cab"], "h01119aebg74bfg4f3bg8946g513d15edc176": ["To insatiable urges.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "9bf7ac9c-d79d-41b0-c068-9932df88d0e7"], "h4216cccaga781g44b3ga062g2fbeee74ade2": ["I wouldn't dream of missing it.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "b829fb4d-df7c-76ae-4374-0cc364c1b5d3"], "h4e0c02b8gdcf6g4e13g99c3g2c04042a1a2e": ["So eager. I'm surprised it took you this long.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "1e13e3b6-bb0f-64ce-5f58-a5f393d74d70"], "h030a051fg550bg4a65g9b4eg7d532647ed42": ["Did you think I wouldn't show?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "918b87d9-cf59-a176-6f57-dfb290b5ab16"], "h83a8e128g5fb6g4f40gbcd6ge7f141b89b46": ["Lots of people make promises. Few keep them.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "7d8892c3-9f4a-cae3-b2b1-cbcd089231e2"], "h5a1975a0g9661g4639g881bg2e24c6fa73ac": ["<i>Drain the cup in one swallow.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "80632e59-e766-edc3-2c21-0cdf2c872cca"], "h8ae88990gdebbg41b4g87fdg34d25b1adf2c": ["Someone's enthusiastic. Maybe I should have brought a barrel.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "7586be4f-0993-845d-29d5-b514f9642266"], "h348552d2gc51bg4159gabd2g68194515bdaf": ["I was hoping for a toast. Any suggestions?", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithShadowheart.html", "d1e4ea6f-a629-7acd-f5f3-092a848ddf07"]}